			<p>
        Hobbs of Reading has been successfully established on the Oxford Road for over 60 years; we are currently looking to expand our clientele base. We have a reputation for providing a professional service and welcome commercial laundry and dry cleaning.  Many local reputable hairdressers nail salons, restaurants and fancy dress shops regularly use Hobbs.  We work hard to offer special rates to our loyal customers and welcome new contracts. The service we provide includes a free pick-up and drop-off of all laundry and dry cleaning to our contracted customers.  The management at Hobbs welcomes you to come and speak with us at the address mentioned in the website at your convenience.
        </p>
        <h2>Domestic Laundry:</h2>
		<p>We offer service washes, and also a fully finished (ironed) laundry service.</p>	
        <h2>Commercial Laundry:</h2>
		<p>We offer the highest standard of service on all bed linens, table linens, and any other household items. Although we specialise in Spa salons, Hotels, Guest Houses, and Restaurants.</p>
		<h2> Collection & Delivery Service</h2>
		<p>We offer collection and delivery service in Reading including other locations through contracted agreements with Hobbs management. If you're looking for a high quality and competitive laundry service, please contact us today. We value our customers highly and take pride in the standard of commercial laundry services we offer.
